msgstr "qt6options(7)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developer's Guide to &kalarm;"
msgstr "Utvecklingsguide för &kalarm;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; provides an interface to allow other applications to request the "
"following functions:"
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; tillhandahåller ett gränssnitt som låter andra program begära "
"följande funktioner:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3739
#, no-c-format
msgid "cancel an already scheduled alarm"
msgstr "avbryt ett redan schemalagt alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3740
#, no-c-format
msgid "trigger an already scheduled alarm"
msgstr "aktivera ett redan schemalagt alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3741
#, no-c-format
msgid "display the Alarm Edit dialog"
msgstr "visa dialogrutan för alarmredigering"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3742
#, no-c-format
msgid "list scheduled alarms"
msgstr "Lista schemalagda alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each of the above functions is implemented both by a &DBus; call and by the "
"command line. &DBus; calls should be used in preference if &kalarm; is "
"already running."
msgstr ""
"Var och en av de ovannämnda funktionerna implementeras både som ett &DBus; "
"anrop och via kommandoraden. D-Bus anrop är att föredra om &kalarm; redan "
"kör."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3750
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Interface"
msgstr "&DBus; gränssnitt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &DBus; calls described in this document are all implemented in "
"&kalarm;'s <constant>/kalarm</constant> &DBus; object path. The interface is "
"defined in the files <filename>org.kde.kalarm.kalarm.xml</filename> and "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>."
msgstr ""
"&DBus; anropen som beskrivs i det här dokumentet är alla implementerade i "
"&kalarm;s &DBus; objektsökväg <constant>/kalarm</constant>. Gränssnittet är "
"definierat i filerna <filename>org.kde.kalarm.kalarm.xml</filename> och "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>cancelEvent</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>cancelEvent</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3763
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>cancelEvent</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>cancelEvent</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid "cancel an already scheduled alarm."
msgstr "avbryt ett redan schemalagt alarm."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:3767
#, no-c-format
msgid "void cancelEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>eventID</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"void cancelEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>händelse-ID</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3770 index.docbook:3807 index.docbook:3853 index.docbook:4081
#: index.docbook:4279 index.docbook:4444 index.docbook:4640 index.docbook:4808
#: index.docbook:4854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parametrar"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3773 index.docbook:3810 index.docbook:4811
#, no-c-format
msgid "eventID"
msgstr "händelse-ID"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the unique ID of the event to be canceled, optionally prefixed by "
"the configuration name or numeric ID of the resource containing the event, "
"in the format <replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Anger unikt ID för händelsen som ska avbrytas, valfritt inledd med "
"konfigurationsnamnet eller numeriskt ID för resursen som innehåller "
"händelsen på formatet <replaceable>[resurs-ID:]händelse-ID</replaceable>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3786 index.docbook:3823 index.docbook:4047 index.docbook:4253
#: index.docbook:4418 index.docbook:4613 index.docbook:4785 index.docbook:4831
#: index.docbook:4886 index.docbook:4916
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Beskrivning</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>cancelEvent()</function> is a &DBus; call to cancel the specified "
"alarm. &kalarm; deletes the alarm from the calendar without displaying or "
"executing it."
msgstr ""
"<function>cancelEvent()</function> är ett &DBus; anrop för att avbryta det "
"angivna alarmet. &kalarm; tar bort alarmet från kalendern utan att visa "
"eller köra det."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3797
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>triggerEvent</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>triggerEvent</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>triggerEvent</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>triggerEvent</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid "trigger an already scheduled alarm."
msgstr "aktivera ett redan schemalagt alarm."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:3804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void triggerEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>eventID</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"void triggerEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>händelse-ID</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the unique ID of the event to be triggered, optionally prefixed by "
"the configuration name or numeric ID of the resource containing the event, "
"in the format <replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Anger unikt ID för händelsen som ska utlösas, valfritt inledd med "
"konfigurationsnamnet eller numeriskt ID för resursen som innehåller "
"händelsen på formatet <replaceable>[resurs-ID:]händelse-ID</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>triggerEvent()</function> is a &DBus; call to trigger the "
"immediate display or execution of the specified alarm (regardless of what "
"time it is scheduled for). &kalarm; retrieves the alarm from the calendar "
"and then displays or executes it."
msgstr ""
"<function>triggerEvent()</function> är ett &DBus; anrop för att aktivera "
"omedelbar visning eller körning av det angivna alarmet (oberoende av vilken "
"tid det är schemalagt). &kalarm; hämtar alarmet från kalendern och visar det "
"eller kör det."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm is already due, &kalarm; then deletes all scheduled occurrences "
"of the alarm up to the current time, and if no repetitions of the alarm "
"still remain, the alarm is deleted from the calendar. If the alarm is not "
"due yet, its scheduled occurrences are left unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Om alarmet redan ska aktiveras, tar &kalarm; sedan bort alla schemalagda "
"händelser för alarmet fram till nuvarande tid, och om inga upprepningar av "
"alarmet fortfarande finns kvar, så tas alarmet bort från kalendern. Om "
"alarmet inte ska aktiveras ännu, så lämnas dess schemalagda händelser "
"oförändrade."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3841
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleMessage</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleMessage</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3844
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>scheduleMessage</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>scheduleMessage</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:3845
#, no-c-format
msgid "schedule a new alarm message."
msgstr "schemalägg ett nytt alarm."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:3848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleMessage(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>message</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>, \n"
