"replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>, \n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>bg</replaceable>, \n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>fg</replaceable>, \n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>teckensnitt</"
"replaceable>, \n"
"                     const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>ljudadress</"
"replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>påminnelse</replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>upprepningstyp</replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>upprepningsintervall</replaceable>, \n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>slut_datum_tid</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3856 index.docbook:4084 index.docbook:4282 index.docbook:4447
#: index.docbook:4643
#, no-c-format
msgid "name"
msgstr "namn"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3858 index.docbook:4086 index.docbook:4284 index.docbook:4449
#: index.docbook:4645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies an optional name for the alarm."
msgstr "Anger ett valfritt namn på alarmet."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3863 index.docbook:4478
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>message</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>meddelande</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the text of the message to be scheduled, or if <parameter>flags</"
"parameter> has the <userinput>DISPLAY_COMMAND</userinput> bit set, specifies "
"the command line to execute to generate the message text."
msgstr ""
"Anger texten i meddelandet att schemalägga, eller om <parameter>flaggor</"
"parameter> har biten <userinput>DISPLAY_COMMAND</userinput>, anger "
"kommandoraden att köra för att skapa texten i meddelandet."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3873 index.docbook:4099 index.docbook:4298 index.docbook:4493
#: index.docbook:4665
#, no-c-format
msgid "startDateTime"
msgstr "startdatum_tid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3875 index.docbook:4101 index.docbook:4300 index.docbook:4495
#: index.docbook:4667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the scheduled date, or date and time, at which the message should "
"be displayed. For a date-only alarm, the string should be in the format "
"<replaceable>YYYY-MM-DD[ TZ]</replaceable> (as returned by "
"<methodname>QDate::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). For an alarm with a "
"date and time, the string should be in the format <replaceable>YYYY-MM-DDTHH:"
"MM[:SS][ TZ]</replaceable> (as returned by <methodname>QDateTime::"
"toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>) or <replaceable>HH:MM[:SS]</replaceable> "
"(as returned by <methodname>QTime::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). If "
"no date is specified, today's date is used. Note that any seconds value is "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"Anger schemalagt datum, eller datum och tid, då meddelandet ska visas. "
"Strängen ska vara på formatet <replaceable>ÅÅÅÅ-MM-DD[ TZ]</replaceable> för "
"ett alarm med bara datum (som returneras av <methodname>QDate::toString(Qt::"
"ISODate)</methodname>). För ett alarm med ett datum och en tid, ska strängen "
"vara på formatet <replaceable>ÅÅÅÅ-MM-DDTTT:MM[:SS][ TZ]</replaceable> (som "
"returneras av <methodname>QDateTime::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>) "
"eller <replaceable>TT:MM[:SS]</replaceable> (som returneras av "
"<methodname>QTime::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). Om inget datum "
"anges, används dagens datum. Observera att ett eventuellt sekundvärde "
"ignoreras."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3887 index.docbook:4113 index.docbook:4312 index.docbook:4507
#: index.docbook:4679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no time zone is specified, the local system time zone is assumed. If a "
"time zone specifier <replaceable>TZ</replaceable> is present, it may be the "
"name of a system time zone (&eg; <userinput>Europe/London</userinput>), or "
"<userinput>UTC</userinput> representing the UTC time zone."
msgstr ""
"Om någon tidszon inte anges, förutsätts att den lokala systemtidszonen ska "
"användas. Om en tidszonangivelse <replaceable>TZ</replaceable> finns med, "
"kan det vara namnet på en systemtidszon (t.ex. <userinput>Europe/London</"
"userinput>) eller <userinput>UTC</userinput> som representerar tidszonen UTC."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3896 index.docbook:4122 index.docbook:4321 index.docbook:4516
#: index.docbook:4688
#, no-c-format
msgid "lateCancel"
msgstr "avbryt_försenat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3898 index.docbook:4124 index.docbook:4323 index.docbook:4518
#: index.docbook:4690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the alarm to be canceled if it cannot be triggered within the "
"specified number of minutes after the alarm's scheduled time. If the value "
"is 0, the alarm will not be canceled no matter how late it is triggered."
msgstr ""
"Gör att alarmet avbryts om det inte kan visas inom angivet antal minuter "
"efter alarmets schemalagda tid. Om värdet är 0, avbryts inte alarmet "
"oberoende av hur sent det visas."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3906 index.docbook:4132 index.docbook:4331 index.docbook:4526
#: index.docbook:4698
#, no-c-format
msgid "flags"
msgstr "flaggor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to message alarms."
msgstr ""
"Anger logiskt eller av de önskade alarmflaggorna. Flaggbitarna är "
"definierade i klassen <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> i "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Observera att alla flaggbitar inte "
"gäller meddelandealarm."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3916 index.docbook:4142
#, no-c-format
msgid "bgColor"
msgstr "bg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3918
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the background color for displaying the message. The string may be "
"in the format <quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (as returned by <methodname>QColor::"
"name()</methodname>) where RR, GG and BB are two-digit hexadecimal values "
"for red, green and blue. Alternatively the string may be in any of the other "
"formats accepted by <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, such "
"as a name from the X color database (&eg; <quote>red</quote> or "
"<quote>steelblue</quote>). Set the string to null to specify the current "
"default background color."
msgstr ""
"Anger bakgrundsfärg för att visa meddelandet. Formatet på strängen kan vara "
"<quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (som returneras av <methodname>QColor::name()</"
"methodname>), där RR, GG och BB är tvåsiffrors hexadecimala värden för röd, "
"grön och blå. Alternativt kan strängen vara något av de andra format som "
"accepteras av <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, såsom ett "
"namn från X-färgdatabasen (t.ex. <quote>red</quote> eller <quote>steelblue</"
"quote>). Ange strängens värde som null för att välja aktuell förvald "
"bakgrundsfärg."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3931
#, no-c-format
msgid "fgColor"
msgstr "fg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the foreground color for displaying the message. The format of the "
"string is the same as for <parameter>bgColor</parameter>, or alternatively "
"set the string to null to specify the current default foreground color."
msgstr ""
"Anger förgrundsfärg för att visa meddelandet. Formatet på strängen är samma "
"som för <parameter>bg</parameter>, eller alternativt kan strängens värde "
"anges som null för att välja aktuell förvald förgrundsfärg."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid "font"
msgstr "teckensnitt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the font for displaying the message. The format of the string is "
"that output by <methodname>QFont::toString()</methodname>. Set the string to "
"null to use the default message font current at the time the message is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Anger teckensnittet för att visa meddelandet. Strängens format är det som "
"skrivs ut med <methodname>QFont::toString()</methodname>. Ange strängens "
"värde som null för att använda förvalt teckensnitt för meddelanden som "
"gäller vid tiden då meddelandet visas."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3951 index.docbook:4157 index.docbook:4650
#, no-c-format
msgid "audioURL"
msgstr "ljudadress"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3953 index.docbook:4159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the audio file which is to be played when the message is "
"displayed. Set the value to null if no audio file is to be played."
msgstr ""
"Anger ljudfilen som ska spelas när meddelandet visas. Ange värdet null om "
"ingen ljudfil ska spelas."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3960 index.docbook:4166
#, no-c-format
msgid "reminderMins"
msgstr "påminnelse_minuter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3962 index.docbook:4168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of minutes in advance of the main alarm and of each of "
"its recurrences (if any) at which a reminder alarm should be displayed. "
"Specify a negative value for a reminder to be displayed after the main "
"alarm. Specify 0 if no reminder is required."
msgstr ""
"Anger antal minuter i förväg innan huvudalarmet och varje upprepning (om det "
"finns någon) som påminnelsen ska visas. Ange ett negativt värde för en "
"påminnelse som ska visas efter huvudalarmet. Ange 0 om ingen påminnelse "
"krävs."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3970 index.docbook:4176 index.docbook:4341 index.docbook:4536
#: index.docbook:4708
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurrence"
msgstr "upprepning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3972 index.docbook:4178 index.docbook:4343 index.docbook:4538
#: index.docbook:4710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies a regular recurrence for the alarm, using iCalendar syntax as "
"defined in <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>. For example, <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;INTERVAL=3;"
"BYDAY=-1MO</quote> would specify 4 repetitions at 3-monthly intervals on the "
"last Monday of the month. For a non-recurring alarm, specify an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Anger en regelbunden upprepning av alarmet, med iCalendar-syntax som "
"definieras av <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>. Till exempel skulle <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;"
"INTERVAL=3;BYDAY=-1MO</quote> ange fyra upprepningar med "
"tremånadersintervall den sista måndagen i månaden. För ett alarm som inte "
"ska upprepas, ange en tom sträng."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3983 index.docbook:4189 index.docbook:4354 index.docbook:4549
#: index.docbook:4721
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurType"
msgstr "upprepningstyp"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3985 index.docbook:4191 index.docbook:4356 index.docbook:4551
#: index.docbook:4723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the recurrence type for the alarm. The permissible values are "
"MINUTELY, DAILY, WEEKLY, MONTHLY, YEARLY. These are defined in class "
"<classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. "
"Monthly recurrences are of the day of the month type, and yearly recurrences "
"are of the date in the year type, with the date in both cases taken from the "
"<parameter>startDateTime</parameter> parameter."
msgstr ""
"Anger alarmets upprepningstyp. Tillåtna värden är MINUTELY, DAILY, WEEKLY, "
"MONTHLY, YEARLY. Dessa definieras i klassen <classname>KAlarmIface</"
"classname> i <filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Månatliga upprepningar är "
"av typen dagen under månaden, och årliga upprepningar är av typen datum "
"under året, där datumet i båda fall tas från väljaren "
"<parameter>startdatum_tid</parameter>."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3996 index.docbook:4202 index.docbook:4367 index.docbook:4562
#: index.docbook:4734
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurInterval"
msgstr "upprepningsintervall"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3998 index.docbook:4204 index.docbook:4369 index.docbook:4564
#: index.docbook:4736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of periods (minutes/days/weeks/months/years as "
"specified by <parameter>recurType</parameter>) between recurrences of the "
"alarm."
msgstr ""
"Anger antal perioder (minuter/dagar/veckor/månader/år som anges av "
"<parameter>upprepningstyp</parameter>) mellan upprepningar av alarmet."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4006 index.docbook:4212 index.docbook:4377 index.docbook:4572
#: index.docbook:4744
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurCount"
msgstr "upprepningsantal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4008 index.docbook:4214 index.docbook:4379 index.docbook:4574
#: index.docbook:4746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of times that the alarm should be repeated. Specify -1 "
"to repeat the alarm indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"Anger antalet gånger som alarmet ska upprepas. Ange -1 för att upprepa "
"alarmet för evigt."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4014 index.docbook:4220 index.docbook:4385 index.docbook:4580
#: index.docbook:4752
#, no-c-format
msgid "endDateTime"
msgstr "slut_datum_tid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4016 index.docbook:4222 index.docbook:4387 index.docbook:4582
#: index.docbook:4754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the end date, or date and time, for recurrences of the alarm. If "
"<parameter>startDateTime</parameter> includes a time, this parameter must "
"also include a time; if <parameter>startDateTime</parameter> contains only a "
"date, this parameter must also contain only a date. It must not contain a "
"time zone specifier; the same time zone as for <parameter>startDateTime</"
"parameter> is used to interpret this parameter's value."
msgstr ""
"Anger slutdatum, eller datum och tid, för alarmets upprepningar. Om "
"<parameter>startdatum_tid</parameter> innehåller en tid, måste den här "
"väljaren också innehålla en tid. Om <parameter>startdatum_tid</parameter> "
"bara innehåller ett datum, måste den här väljaren också bara innehålla ett "
"datum. Den får inte innehålla en specifikation av tidzon: samma tidzon som i "
"<parameter>startdatum_tid</parameter> används för att tolka parameterns "
"värde."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4027 index.docbook:4233 index.docbook:4398 index.docbook:4593
#: index.docbook:4765
#, no-c-format
msgid "subRepeatInterval"
msgstr "delrepetition_intervall"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4029 index.docbook:4235 index.docbook:4400 index.docbook:4595
#: index.docbook:4767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of minutes between sub-repetitions of the alarm. "
"Specify 0 for no sub-repetition. Ignored if no recurrence is specified."
msgstr ""
"Anger antalet minuter mellan delrepetitioner av alarmet. Ange 0 för ingen "
"delrepetition. Ignoreras om ingen upprepning är angiven."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4036 index.docbook:4242 index.docbook:4407 index.docbook:4602
#: index.docbook:4774
#, no-c-format
msgid "subRepeatCount"
msgstr "delrepetition_antal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4038 index.docbook:4244 index.docbook:4409 index.docbook:4604
#: index.docbook:4776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of sub-repetitions of the alarm, including the initial "
"occurrence."
msgstr ""
"Anger antalet delrepetitioner av alarmet, inklusive ursprunglig aktivering."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleMessage()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified alarm message for display at the specified date and time. It has "
"three forms. The most general form allows an arbitrary recurrence to be "
"specified &ndash; use this also for non-repeating alarms. The other forms "
"provide convenient access to a restricted set of alarm recurrence types, one "
"specifying a repetition count and the other an end time."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleMessage()</function> är ett &DBus; anrop för att "
"schemalägga det angivna alarmmeddelandet för visning vid det angivna datumet "
"och tiden. Det har tre former. De mest generella formen tillåter att en "
"godtycklig upprepning anges. Använd den också för alarm som inte upprepas. "
"De övriga formerna tillhandahåller bekväm åtkomst till en begränsad mängd "
"upprepningstyper, den ena anger ett upprepningsantal och den andra en "
"sluttid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the scheduled time (including any repetitions) has already passed, "
"&kalarm; immediately displays the message (unless the <parameter>lateCancel</"
"parameter> value indicates that it is now too late to display the alarm, in "
"which case &kalarm; ignores the request). If the scheduled time (or a "
"repetition) is in the future, &kalarm; adds the alarm message to the default "
"active alarm calendar for later display."
msgstr ""
"Om den schemalagda tiden (inklusive eventuella upprepningar) redan har gått "
"ut, visar  &kalarm; omedelbart meddelandet (om inte värdet "
"<parameter>avbryt_försenat</parameter> anger att det nu är för sent att visa "
"alarmet, då &kalarm; ignorerar begäran). Om den schemalagda tiden (eller en "
"upprepning) är i framtiden, lägger &kalarm; till alarmmeddelandet i den "
"förvalda aktiva alarmkalendern för att visas senare."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:4068
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleFile</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleFile</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:4071
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>scheduleFile</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>scheduleFile</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:4072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"schedule a new alarm which displays the contents of a text or image file."
msgstr ""
"schemalägg ett nytt alarm som visar innehållet i en text- eller bildfil."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>URL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                  unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bgColor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>audioURL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>reminderMins</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>recurrence</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>subRepeatInterval</replaceable>, \n"
"                  int <replaceable>subRepeatCount</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>webbadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bg</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>ljudadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>påminnelse</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>upprepning</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>delrepetition_intervall</replaceable>, \n"
"                  int <replaceable>delrepetition_antal</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>URL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                  unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bgColor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>audioURL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>reminderMins</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>recurType</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>recurInterval</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>recurCount</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>webbadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bg</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>ljudadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>påminnelse</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>upprepningstyp</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>upprepningsintervall</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>upprepningsantal</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>URL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                  unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bgColor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>audioURL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>reminderMins</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>recurType</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>recurInterval</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>endDateTime</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>webbadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bg</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const KUrl&amp; <replaceable>ljudadress</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>påminnelse</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>upprepningstyp</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>upprepningsintervall</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>slut_datum_tid</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>URL</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>webbadress</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the text or image file whose contents are to be displayed in the "
"message to be scheduled."
msgstr ""
"Anger text- eller bildfilen vars innehåll ska visas i meddelandet som "
"schemaläggs."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to file alarms."
msgstr ""
"Anger logiskt eller av de önskade alarmflaggorna. Flaggbitarna är "
"definierade i klassen <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> i "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Observera att alla flaggbitar inte "
"gäller filalarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the background color for displaying the file. The string may be in "
"the format <quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (as returned by <methodname>QColor::"
"name()</methodname>) where RR, GG and BB are two-digit hexadecimal values "
"for red, green and blue. Alternatively the string may be in any of the other "
"formats accepted by <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, such "
"as a name from the X color database (&eg; <quote>red</quote> or "
"<quote>steelblue</quote>). Set the string to null to specify the current "
"default background color."
msgstr ""
"Anger bakgrundsfärg för att visa filen. Formatet på strängen kan vara "
"<quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (som returneras av <methodname>QColor::name()</"
"methodname>), där RR, GG och BB är tvåsiffrors hexadecimala värden för röd, "
"grön och blå. Alternativt kan strängen vara något av de andra format som "
"accepteras av <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, såsom ett "
"namn från X-färgdatabasen (t.ex. <quote>red</quote> eller <quote>steelblue</"
"quote>). Ange strängens värde som null för att välja aktuell förvald "
"bakgrundsfärg."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleFile()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified text or image file for display at the specified date and time. "
"Apart from specifying a file path or &URL; and omitting the foreground color "
"and font, its usage is identical to <link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip"
"\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></link> - see the description of that "
"function for further details."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleFile()</function> är ett &DBus; anrop för att schemalägga "
"en angiven text- eller bildfil för visning vid det angivna datumet och "
"tiden. Förutom att ange ett filnamn eller webbadress, och utelämna färg och "
"teckensnitt, är användningen identisk med <link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-"
"descrip\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></link> - se beskrivningen av "
"den funktionen för ytterligare detaljer."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:4266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleCommand</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleCommand</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:4269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>scheduleCommand</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>scheduleCommand</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:4270 index.docbook:4631
#, no-c-format
msgid "schedule a new alarm which executes a shell command."
msgstr "schemalägg ett nytt alarm som kör ett skalkommando."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleCommand(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>commandLine</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>recurrence</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>subRepeatInterval</replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>subRepeatCount</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleAudio(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>ljudwebbadress</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>volymprocent</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                   unsigned <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>upprepning</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>delupprepningsintervall</replaceable>, \n"
"                   int <replaceable>delupprepningsantal</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleCommand(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>commandLine</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurType</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurInterval</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurCount</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleAudio(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>ljudwebbadress</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>volymprocent</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                   unsigned <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>upprepningstyp</replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>upprepningsintervall</replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>upprepningsantal</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleCommand(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>commandLine</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurType</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurInterval</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>endDateTime</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleAudio(const QString&amp; <replaceable>namn</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>ljudwebbadress</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>volymprocent</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>startdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>avbryt_försenat</replaceable>,\n"
"                   unsigned <replaceable>flaggor</replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>upprepningstyp</replaceable>,\n"
"                   int <replaceable>upprepningsintervall</replaceable>,\n"
"                   const QString&amp; <replaceable>slutdatum_tid</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4289
#, no-c-format
msgid "commandLine"
msgstr "kommandorad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the command whose execution is to be scheduled. The "
"<parameter>flags</parameter> parameter indicates whether this parameter "
"contains a shell command line or a command script."
msgstr ""
"Anger kommandot vars körning ska schemaläggas. Väljaren<parameter>flags</"
"parameter> anger om väljaren innehåller en skalkommandorad eller ett "
"kommandoskript."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4333 index.docbook:4700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to command alarms."
msgstr ""
"Anger logiskt eller av de önskade alarmflaggorna. Flaggbitarna är "
"definierade i klassen <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> i "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Observera att alla flaggbitar inte "
"gäller kommandoalarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleCommand()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified shell command line, or command script, for execution at the "
"specified date and time. Apart from specifying a command and omitting the "
"message color, font and audio file parameters, its usage is identical to "
"<link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip\"><function>scheduleMessage</"
"function></link> - see the description of that function for further details."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleCommand()</function> är ett &DBus; anrop för att "
"schemalägga en angiven skalkommandorad, eller kommandoskript, för körning "
"vid det angivna datumet och tiden. Förutom att ange ett kommando och "
"utelämna meddelandets färg, teckensnitt och ljudfil, är användningen "
"identisk med <link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip"
"\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></link> - se beskrivningen av den "
"funktionen för ytterligare detaljer."

